config BR2_PACKAGE_SINGULARITY_DESKTOP_DATA
	bool "singularity-desktop-data"
	help
	  Top-level Singularity desktop data: the dev.sinty.desktop
	  GSettings schema (required by the shell), the xdg-desktop-portal
	  config, the polkit-agent and portal systemd user units, the
	  accountsservice interface and the brand emblem icon.

	  These live in the singularity-desktop meta repository, outside
	  any subprojct, so they are shipped as a standalone package. I
	  might improve it.

	  https://github.com/singularityos-lab/singularity-desktop
